                "parameters": {
                    "content": "## Long Task Handler (Heartbeat)\n\n**Task Name:** task_long_batch\n- Splits task into units\n- Processes units in batches\n- Checks remaining lease time\n- Extends lease via heartbeat_task when needed\n\n**Expected taskData fields (optional):**\n- units: array of units to process\n- totalUnits: number (if units not provided)\n- batchSize: number\n- leaseExpiresAt / lease_expires_at: ISO timestamp\n- leaseBufferMs: number\n- extendByInterval: interval string (e.g., '5 minutes')",
